"content": "<h2>Privacy to conduct conversations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:17\">JER 37:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:22\">1SA 18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:27\">2SA 3:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer40:15\">JER 40:15</a></p>\n<h2>Privacy to express emotions</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:30\">GEN 43:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:9-Matt14:13\">MAT 14:9–14:13</a></p>\n<h2>Privacy to teach and to learn</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:19\">MAT 17:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:28\">MRK 9:28</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:3\">MAT 24:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:3\">MRK 13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:23\">LUK 10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:2\">GAL 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Privacy to pray</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:18\">LUK 9:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5-Matt6:6\">MAT 6:5–6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:22-Matt14:23\">MAT 14:22–14:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:45-Mark6:46\">MRK 6:45–6:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:36\">MAT 26:36</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:32\">MRK 14:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:39-Luke22:42\">LUK 22:39–22:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:12\">LUK 6:12</a></p>",
